TESTING ANALYSIS RULES:
- Use simple text-based approaches for checking test results
- Avoid HTML report viewers (playwright show-report) during development
- Prefer --reporter=line or --reporter=json for clean output
- If port conflicts occur (EADDRINUSE), switch to file-based analysis
- Don't get stuck on fancy reporting - simple works better
- Check for running processes before trying to start servers
